WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.350
When I awoke I was grasping a gun.

00:02.910 --> 00:06.240
The smell of death and metal woke me.

00:06.880 --> 00:08.510
I don’t understand it anymore.

00:08.910 --> 00:10.670
I’m absolutely crazy.

00:11.330 --> 00:12.060
I got scared.

00:12.060 --> 00:15.570
I took the gun, put it in a shopping bag, and hid it in a desk drawer.

00:16.120 --> 00:18.250
There’s a key to the drawer, but it isn’t any good.

00:19.040 --> 00:19.780
Je sais.

00:19.780 --> 00:21.780
I’ll hide it inside of Dad.
